# Film Recommendation Web Application

## Overview

This project is a **simple web application** designed to provide film recommendations using content-based filtering. The application helps users discover new movies by suggesting films similar to those they have enjoyed.

## Key Features

- **Content-Based Filtering:** 
  - Analyzes the films that users have liked.
  - Provides 10 personalized recommendations for similar movies.

- **User-Friendly Interface:** 
  - Developed using **Python**, **Flask**, and **Scikit-learn**.
  - Features an easy-to-navigate interface.

## Objective

The goal of this application is to offer users an easy way to find movies that match their tastes and preferences, enhancing their film-watching experience.
